#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk5
#: ekos-focus.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guilabel>Mechanics Tab Parameters</guilabel>: This sets the parameters in the <link linkend=\"focus-mechanics\">Focus Mechanics</link> pane of the Focus screen. By hovering the mouse over this label you can see in the tooltip what values Focus Advisor is recommending."
msgid "<guilabel>Mechanics Parameters</guilabel>: This sets the parameters in <link linkend=\"focus-mechanics\">Focus Mechanics</link>. By hovering the mouse over this label you can see in the tooltip what values Focus Advisor is recommending."
