#: ekos-focus.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid "The focus display, displays a FITS viewer window onto the frame taken during the focus process. If <guilabel>Ring Mask</guilabel> is selected, then the mask is drawn on the image. All the stars detected by Ekos based on the selected parameters, have their HFR value displayed next to the associated star (unless Measure is set to FWHM)."
